## Executive Overview

The BOEING 220-X represents the first fully integrated aerospace demonstrator built upon the combined foundations of the PI220 ecosystem.

Where earlier programs validated individual technologies, the Boeing 220-X was conceived as the first platform to unify:

* PI220 CORE
* NEO CORE NODE
* X2M Kinetic Modeling Engine
* NEO Turbine
* STARFRAME SF-1
* AFAT-X10

into a single aerospace architecture.

The Boeing 220-X was not intended as a production aircraft.

Its primary purpose was system convergence.

The platform served as the engineering bridge between theoretical architectures and operational aerospace integration.

